sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant FlaskAPI
    participant Camera
    participant PyTorchModel
    
    User->>Frontend: Clicks "Capture Image"
    Frontend->>FlaskAPI: POST /predict_camera
    FlaskAPI->>Camera: Request Frame
    Camera-->>FlaskAPI: Return JPEG Bytes
    FlaskAPI->>FlaskAPI: Base64 Decode & PIL Open
    FlaskAPI->>FlaskAPI: Apply Inference Transform (Resize/Normalize)
    FlaskAPI->>PyTorchModel: Forward Pass (Tensor)
    PyTorchModel-->>FlaskAPI: Logits / Softmax Probabilities
    FlaskAPI->>FlaskAPI: Get Top-1 and Top-3 Classes
    FlaskAPI->>FlaskAPI: Lookup Treatment Recommendations
    FlaskAPI-->>Frontend: JSON Response (Class, Confidence, Treatment)
    Frontend-->>User: Display Results & Recommendations
